=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-01-31b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?fit=1499%2C1640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1499,1640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-01-31b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?fit=274%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?fit=758%2C829&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-24706\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?resize=758%2C830&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"830\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?resize=274%2C300&amp;ssl=1 274w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?resize=936%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 936w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?resize=768%2C840&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?resize=1404%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1404w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1989-01-31b.png?w=1499&amp;ssl=1 1499w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1991:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/11/24/roll-of-the-dice-loose-change/\">Loose Change</a>&#8221; at The Record Plant in Los Angeles.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Loose Change (Studio Outtake - 1991)\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/a6-0mHMgnag?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1997:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his final of four solo acoustic shows in Tokyo. He won&#8217;t perform in Japan again (at least to date).</p>\n<div id=\"v-kHAishzR-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/kHAishzR?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1998:\u00a0</strong><em>Come Together,</em> a special benefit concert for the Sergeant Patrick King Memorial Fund, gathers Bruce, Jon Bon Jovi, Little Steven, Southside Johnny, Max Weinberg, Bobby Bandiera and others at the Count Basie Theater in Red Bank, New Jersey. King was a police officer from Long Branch who was killed two months prior while on duty.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"This Time It&#039;s for Real - January 31, 1998\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cwoiZmmK1Ag?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bon Jovi, Bruce Springsteen &amp; Friends - Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out (Red Bank 1998)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BcYpR2hBYbg?list=PLnbVaK2f4ragU1imlJsn3u_BpNNLzfo7l\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bon Jovi, Springsteen &amp; Friends Come Together - Red Bank 1998 (FULL SHOW)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LYFmmshcwWc?start=1515&#038;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"24708\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-01-31-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?fit=1376%2C802&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1376,802\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1579032898&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-01-31\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?fit=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?fit=758%2C442&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-24708\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?resize=758%2C442&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?resize=1024%2C597&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?resize=768%2C448&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1998-01-31.jpg?w=1376&amp;ssl=1 1376w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>E Street Radio&#8217;s limited-run engagement comes to an end on Sirius Satellite Radio, but it will return more than a year-and-a-half later.</p>\n<p><strong>2010:\u00a0</strong>Bruce wins the Grammy Award for Best Solo Rock Vocal Performance for &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/07/04/roll-of-the-dice-working-on-a-dream/\">Working on a Dream</a>,&#8221; the only one of his four nominations this year to earn him an award. Bruce was also nominated for Best Pop Collaboration with Vocals for &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/01/12/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-rosanne-cash/\">Sea of Heartbreak</a>&#8221; with Rosanne Cash; Best Rock Song for &#8220;Working on a Dream,&#8221; and Best Song Written for a Motion Picture for &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/10/31/roll-of-the-dice-the-wrestler/\">The Wrestler.</a>&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>The River Tour (2016 edition) makes a stop at the Prudential Center in Newark, where &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/04/11/roll-of-the-dice-lonesome-day/\">Lonesome Day</a>,&#8221; &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/01/11/roll-of-the-dice-working-on-the-highway/\">Working on the Highway</a>,&#8221; and &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/06/04/roll-of-the-dice-atlantic-city/\">Atlantic City</a>&#8221; make their tour debuts.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - 2016-01-31 Newark - Meet Me In The City\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SBz7CTnx6gw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - 2016-01-31 Newark - Point Blank\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6TlyZci9od0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Stolen Car - Bruce Springsteen (HD)  Newark, 2016-01-31\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UfyfbYLp64A?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Wrecking Ball (Newark 1/31/16)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mhu4nDpcFfA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-i